descp2: nd-array or sparse matrix Input object to check / convert. Must be two-dimensional and square, otherwise a ValueError will be raised. tol : float Absolute tolerance for equivalence of arrays. Default = 1E-10. raise_warning : boolean (default=True) If True then raise a warning if conversion is required. raise_exception : boolean (default=False) If True then raise an exception if array is not symmetric.

nd-array or sparse matrix Input object to check / convert. Must be two-dimensional and square, otherwise a ValueError will be raised. tol : float Absolute tolerance for equivalence of arrays. Default = 1E-10. raise_warning : boolean (default=True) If True then raise a warning if conversion is required. raise_exception : boolean (default=False) If True then raise an exception if array is not symmetric.
